snippet.title: Element TD 2 Official Release Trailer
snippet.description:
After 13 months in Early Access, Element TD 2 has Officially Released!
Buy it on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1018830/Element_TD_2__Multiplayer_Tower_Defense/

Music: Warriors - Dark Fantasy Studio
